## Installation

To install `lambda-dev-server`, use pip:

```sh
pip install lambda-dev-server
```

## Usage

```bash
# Given a Lambda handler named handler in app.py
lambda-dev-server app.handler
```

## Debbuging

```json
{
  "version": "0.2.0",
  "configurations": [
    {
      "name": "Python Debugger: Module",
      "type": "debugpy",
      "request": "launch",
      "module": "lambda_dev_server",
      "args": ["app.handler"]
    }
  ]
}
```

